<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Welcome to CLIQK</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">
  <div style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px 20px;">

    <h2 style="color:#000; font-size:24px; margin-bottom:24px;">
      Hey {{username}},
    </h2>

    <p style="color:#333; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
      Thank you for signing up to CLIQK.
    </p>

    <p style="color:#333; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
      Group chats are where the best conversations happen, so we built a way to let others join in on that vibe.
      Whether you're here to grow your section, connect with your friends, or have a good time scrolling through
      other people's chats – CLIQK is the place for you.
    </p>

    <p style="color:#333; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
      We're still early, and honestly, we can't build the best platform without feedback from people like you.
      If anything feels off, if something could be better, or if you've got ideas – please let us know.
    </p>

    <p style="color:#333; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
      Appreciate you coming on this journey with us.
    </p>

    <p style="color:#333; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
      If you need anything at all, reply to this email or contact me directly at
      <a href="mailto:kennethyao@cliqkworld.com">kennethyao@cliqkworld.com</a>.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top:32px; color:#333;">
      Kenneth Yao<br />
      <span style="color:#666; font-size:14px;">Founder, CLIQK</span>
    </p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
